Real Racing 3: Keroxea Edition
This version was developed to preserve the original state of the game.
The game's size has been efficiently reduced (1.4 GB)
Graphical adjustments have been made to improve game performance.
Compatibility issues have been resolved. The game runs on devices with Adreno GPUs.
The game archiving system was controlled by a Samsung Galaxy Wonder (GT-I8150).
The archive was first tested on Android 4.4.4 KitKat with Cyanogenmod 11 operating system.
This archive was compiled by Qualcomm Snapdragon S2 MSM8255.
GPU: 1x1.4 GHz Scorpion (Adreno 205)
